  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet or wok over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger and stir-fry for 1 minute.",
    "Add the sliced onion and stir-fry for 2 minutes or until it starts to soften.",
    "Add the sliced peruvian aji amarillo peppers and stir-fry for 2 minutes.",
    "Add the pitted olives and stir-fry for 1 minute.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Stir in the chopped fresh cilantro and lime juice.",
    "Serve the stir-fry in a beautiful lacquerware bowl.",
    "Garnish with additional cilantro if desired."
